## ‚ö° Power Consumption

- **Operating voltage**: 5 V  
- **Average current**: 88 mA  
- **Average power**:  
  \[
  P = V \times I = 5 \times 0.088 = \boxed{0.44 \text{ W}}
  \]

---

## üîã Battery Life Estimation

- **Battery**: 5 V, 1000 mAh Li-ion  
- **DC-DC efficiency**: 85%  
- **Effective energy**:  
  
  E = 5 \times 1 \times 0.85 = \boxed{4.25 \text{ Wh}}
  
Runtime  
  
  T = \frac{4.25}{0.44} = \boxed{9.66 \text{ hours}}
  

---

